y, Nippon Steel has committed to relocating its U.S. headquarters to Pittsburgh, where U.S. Steel is currently based, in a bid to alleviate some of the apprehensions surrounding the merger.", "score": 0.5433243, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://abc3340.com/news/nation-world/nippon-steel-and-us-steel-challenge-bidens-block-of-merger-in-court", "title": "Nippon Steel and U.S. Steel challenge Biden\'s block of merger in court", "content": "\\"The companies remain steadfast that the transaction will enhance, not threaten, United States\' national security,\\" they said. \\"Only the companies\' partnership will deliver $55 per share to U.S. Steel stockholders and guarantee the significant capital investments and technology sharing needed to ensure a strong U.S. Steel for generations to come.\\"", "score": 0.3817962, "raw_content": null}]',
